snippet.title: Super Mario Bros 64 Longplay (C64) [2019] [QHD]
snippet.description:
Follow me on Twitter @ https://twitter.com/Al82_Retro
Get Great Retro Scene News @ http://www.vintageisthenewold.com
Developed and released by Zeropaige in 2019

Awesome conversion of the Nintendo platforming classic, this is about as close to perfect replication of Mario on the C64 as you could wish.

Great Giana Sisters fell foul of Nintendo's legal department all those years ago, so nobody expects this to be any different - be sure to hunt the game down before it disappears!

And yes, the game does have all the warp zones - I just chose not to use them!

#c64
#supermario
#retrogaming
